{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：13:43 2026-05-05 HKT<br/>發佈時間：13:43 2026-05-05 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：13:43 2026-05-05 HKT</p><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/394896dea640b1c44a5d762344605fd4/2026-05/2_3_9.jpg\"/><p>龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位，今（5日）早上11時25分，警方接獲多個報案指有單位冒出濃煙，消防接報派員到場救火，其間約100名居民自行疏散，火警約26分鐘後救熄，事件中無人受傷。經初步調查，相信起火原因為單位廚房的抽氣扇短路引致，並無可疑。</p><img alt=\"單位熏黑。蔡楚輝攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e8baf7ef1bf7127405ffc293629145f/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260505_122302578_02.jpg\"/><img alt=\"警員及消防到場。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e53014d98a7d583ccdd563573e28146/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260505_122302578_04.jpg\"/><img alt=\"約100名居民自行疏散。蔡楚輝攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03e1b622b1f38923396cfb17088b34d6/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260505_122302578_07.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f152377fe8a39335a46fca1a03ef83c6/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260505_122302578_09.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-05T05:57:08.907413+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":199,"images":5,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}